 <b>Formal equation.</b> (nom: <tt>equation</tt>)<br>
 The answer is evaluated as an equation and the comparison is done for the variable values in
 the range given by the author, with the author precision.
 
The reply <tt>a = 0</tt> is considered as<tt>a</tt>. With the option
 <tt>eqsign=yes</tt>, the student is obliged to write <tt> a = 0</tt>. 
